<br>
With regards to max Haste, that I do not know for certain, but I recall seeing a reply from someone at Verant (perhaps the spell/effects guy) that max haste was like 95%.<br>
<br>
Regardless, unless you're a monk, where your bare fists get faster and do more damage as you level, I don't believe that your level has anything to do with haste...except perhaps for the fact that you sometrimes have to be of a minimum level (usually 46 or 51) to receive a higher-level (post 50) haste buff.<br>
