<br>
Haste cap does increase with level.  Something like 85% pre50, 95% mid50s, and 105% at 60.  Although rounding makes it effectively 100% at 60.<br>
<br>
There is NO minimum delay.  Take a twig and max haste it, you get 5 delay or less.<br>
<br>
